quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  11,13,"Kaa hara sirkoo…ìe …ìen wi'ay: Muhammadu fefindi Alqur'aana, hara wanaa nde wayahu immorde ka Alla? Maakiran …ìe an Nulaa…óo teeragol: Addee Corteeji(cimooje) sappo yeru ndee Alqur'aanaare, cincaande, hara on hatonjina e ko goonngina …ói sifa Alqur'aana nde aa∆¥i…óon nden ko fefindaande, noddon kala mo ha…ótan…óon ko wallitoron e …óum, si on laatike goongu…ìe e nodditagol wonnde Alqur'aana ko fefindaande."
  11,14,"Si …ìe addaali ko lanndi…óon …ìe kon -tawde …ìe hatta- naani …óum-, haray onon …ìee gom…óim…ìe, anndiree pellital wonnde Alqur'aana ko Alla jippininde e ganndal Makko dow Nulaa…óo Makko on, wanah nde fefindaande. Anndon kadi alah rewe- tee…óo e goonga si wanaa Alla. Hara onon ko on jebbilora- nii…ìe Mo e …óii hujjaaji ta∆¥oral …óoo?"
  11,15,"Kala on taw…óo ko o faandorii golle makko …óen ko nguurnadam aduna e cu…óaari majjam lannoojam, wanah laakara on faandori …óe, Men hunnanay …ìe baraaji golle ma…ì…ìe …óen aduna, Men ye…óa…ìe cellal, e hoolaare, e yaajireede arsike ko aldaa e …óuytaneede huunde e baraaji golle ma…ì…ìe …óin."
  11,16,"∆Åen siforii…ìe nden faandaare ≈ãi√±aande, alanaa…ìe e baraaji √ëalnde Darngal, si wanah naadeede Yiite. Baraaji golle ma…ì…ìe …óen sooya, golle ma…ì…ìe …óen wona meere; tawde …óe ardiniranooka gom…óinal, wanaa faandaare sellunde. ∆Åe faandoranooki golle ma…ì…ìe …óen fii Alla e galle laakara …óen."
  11,17,"Fototah Annabiijo Muhammadu (yo o his) hino wondi e burhaanu immorde ka Joomi makko, hino jokkiti mo seedii…óo immorde ka Joomi makko, on woni Jibriilu. Hino seedanoo mo kadi e Annabaaku makko ngun ko adii, Tawreeta jippinanoonde nden e Muusaa (yo o his), nden …óoworde yim…ìe yurmeende ma…ì…ìe. Kanko e …ìen gom…óim…ìe wonndu…ìe e makko …ìe fotatah e …ìen heefer…ìe yoolii…ìe e majjere; tawde …ìeya kan hino gom…óini Alqur'aana e Muhammadu on mo nde jippinaa e muu…óum. Kala yeddu…óo mo e …óiya diinaaji, haray ko Yiite ngen woni fodoore makko nden √ëalnde Darngal. Wata a laato an Nulaa…óo, e sikkitagol Alqur'aana e kon ko …ìe fadaa. Pellet …óum ko goonga ka sikke alah e mu'un, ko woni tun, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen gom…óintaa, e hoore kon ko …óu…ó…óinaa e dalilaaji …ìanngu…ói."
  11,18,"Alah …ìur…óo too√±ude haa hewta on fefindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, o dammbira Mo sirku maa …ìi…ó…óo. ∆Åen faggitotoo…ìe …óen penaale e hoore Alla, …ìe wee…ìitoyte ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darangal, fii yo O lanndito …ìe golle ma…ì…ìe …óen. Malaa'ikaa…ìe e Nulaa…ìe seedinoo…ìe …ìen wi'a: "Ko …ìee …óoo woni fenunoo…ìe baKki e Alla …ìen, …ìe dammbi e Makko sirku e …ói…ì…ìo. Hey, kuddi Alla ndin wonii e …ìen too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun fenugol e Alla."
  11,19,"∆Åen sakkotoo…ìe yim…ìe …ìen gaay e laawol Ala focciingol ngol, hi…ìe …óa…ì…ìana ngol oo√±aare gaay e foccagol ngol fii wata gooto jokku ngol. Kam…ìe kadi hi…ìe yedda immital …ìaawo maayde."